# tests/

BATS test suite for Intent CLI covering command routing, project initialization, steel thread management, skill/agent systems, and CLI utilities. Tests are organized by functionality with shared helpers for sandbox environments and assertion utilities. Includes unit tests, integration tests, and test fixtures for comprehensive CLI validation.

## Dirs

- `fixtures/` -- Test fixtures and sample files for test scenarios
- `integration/` -- End-to-end workflow tests validating complete user journeys
- `lib/` -- Shared test libraries and helper functions (test_helper.bash)
- `unit/` -- Unit tests for individual commands and subsystems

## Files

- `run_tests.sh` -- Main test runner that executes BATS tests with environment setup
- `core_functionality.bats` -- Essential core functionality tests that must always pass
- `README.md` -- Test suite documentation and running instructions
